HEADWORD: Indogenide
<hw>In"do*gen*ide</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Any one of the derivatives of indogen, which contain that group as
a nucleus.</def>⟦br⟧
